for an honest conversation.

15:18.534 --> 15:19.911
And what do I do?

15:20.912 --> 15:21.955
What do I do best?

15:22.789 --> 15:24.374
I am a journalist.

15:24.457 --> 15:28.294
I can feel when the world needs me
to articulate something for them.

15:28.378 --> 15:30.797
