24:23.246 --> 24:24.247
Absolutely.

24:24.664 --> 24:27.625
We were just discussing the enigma
that is Bradley Jackson.

24:27.709 --> 24:28.918
Fabulous.

24:29.002 --> 24:30.587
So, if you'd give us a few minutes--

24:30.670 --> 24:32.505
No, I'd actually like to get in on that.

24:32.922 --> 24:35.133
-It's actually why I'm here.
