that we are all on the same page.

24:50.064 --> 24:51.441
So I'm gonna be here all weekend.

24:52.358 --> 24:54.110
-All weekend?
-Yeah, all weekend.

24:54.193 --> 24:55.695
Sean typed up a schedule. Sean.

24:55.778 --> 24:57.614
