25:28.478 --> 25:31.522
But I think it's important
that she feels in control of it.

25:31.606 --> 25:33.399
In control of the language used.

25:33.483 --> 25:37.820
So, just to be clear,
and I appreciate the typed-up schedule,

25:38.988 --> 25:41.032
you're doing the Ashley Brown interview?

25:43.576 --> 25:44.911
Yes, I am, Chip.

25:49.374 --> 25:50.458
What?

25:51.751 --> 25:54.462
Okay. All right, team.

25:55.088 --> 25:57.507
I will address the elephant in the room.

26:00.760 --> 26:04.722
Yes, yes. I worked side by side with Mitch
for 15 years.

26:05.265 --> 26:07.100
God knows he was not perfect.

26:07.558 --> 26:09.143
I felt it daily.

26:10.520 --> 26:12.230
But I didn't know he was that guy.

26:13.773 --> 26:15.108
