26:19.487 --> 26:22.490
But I want you to know that I am here now.

26:23.157 --> 26:24.617
And I'm here for Ashley,

26:25.535 --> 26:26.911
and I'm here for you.

26:27.328 --> 26:30.039
I'm available, I'm accessible,
and I'm awake.

26:33.626 --> 26:35.712
So, shall we?

26:39.799 --> 26:44.846
Stay on two. As we said, go with Yanko.
Go with Yanko.

26:44.929 --> 26:47.307
