31:44.520 --> 31:46.981
We ask to be a part of the conversation.

31:47.440 --> 31:48.650
I mean...

31:49.734 --> 31:51.527
we did something wrong, okay.

31:51.945 --> 31:52.946
What?

31:53.029 --> 31:54.656
