32:16.886 --> 32:19.472
Oh, fuck that! Jesus. They did it with us.

32:19.555 --> 32:20.598
"Gotcha!

32:21.391 --> 32:23.726
I'll fuck you for the role,
and then I'll win an Oscar."

32:23.810 --> 32:26.437
