32:26.521 --> 32:29.566
so I'll scream 'rape'
and then I'll force a settlement."

32:29.649 --> 32:32.485
You know,
as if that lazy lay deserves a cent.

32:32.569 --> 32:34.237
No, no, you're wrong.

32:36.114 --> 32:37.323
Wow. Is that real?

32:37.407 --> 32:38.575
"Gotcha!

32:38.658 --> 32:40.868
