in the second wave was just different,

33:55.818 --> 33:59.739
and I don't think
we should be scared to talk about it.

34:04.827 --> 34:07.622
Spell it out for me, won't you, Mitch?

34:15.880 --> 34:18.299
Well, you are actually a predator.

34:19.717 --> 34:21.761
